fxcop)UseSafeHandleToEncapsulateNativeResources6CA2006: Use SafeHandle to encapsulate native resources"MAJOR*cs2CA2006:ı<h2>Cause</h2>
<p>
            Managed code uses <code>IntPtr</code> to access native resources.
